an style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>NH&Acirc;N VẬT TRONG TYNKER</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c; font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>A. Mục ti&ecirc;u hoạt động</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">1- Hiểu được kh&aacute;i niệm đối tượng trong Tynker l&agrave; g&igrave;.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">2- Ph&acirc;n biệt được một số đặc điểm của đối tượng trong&nbsp;Tynker.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">3- Th&agrave;nh thạo c&aacute;c thao t&aacute;c xử l&yacute; đối tượng&nbsp;trong Tynker.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c; font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><strong>B. Video b&agrave;i giảng</strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Phần 1</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/df4207KxWaI\" style=\"width:100%; height:500px\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Phần 2</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/zewbJ0LHnFk\" style=\"width:100%; height:500px\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Phần 3</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/ywY29e8G5II',3,'',7,3,58,154),(136,'Đồ án khác','2019-04-28 16:51:14.736103','2019-04-29 10:17:30.536100',15,1,'<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"background-color:white\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">C&aacute;c em <span style=\"color:black\">xem c&aacute;c</span> đồ &aacute;n kh&aacute;c b&ecirc;n trong file pdf</span></span></span></p>\r\n','','/media/Do_an_khac.pdf',1,'',6,2,68,NULL),(137,'Thuật Toán Trong Stencyl','2019-04-28 16:51:26.539065','2019-04-28 16:51:26.539070',1,1,'<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">Introduce students to &ldquo;logical thinking&rdquo; through programming. Students will learn the following concepts:&nbsp;<br />\r\n● How do computers work?</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">● Control Flow (how a program runs) </span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">● Conditionals (if, else, else-if, boolean statements) </span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">● Logical Operators (equals, and, or, not)&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">Introduce students to &ldquo;logical thinking&rdquo; through programming. Students will learn the following concepts:&nbsp;<br />\r\n● How do computers work?</span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">● Control Flow (how a program runs) </span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">● Conditionals (if, else, else-if, boolean statements) </span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">● Logical Operators (equals, and, or, not)&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\r\n','/media/Lesson2-TeachersGuide.pdf',3,'',5,2,65,NULL),(138,'Vòng Tròn Sự Kiện','2019-04-28 16:52:49.244681','2019-04-28 16:52:49.244686',1,1,'<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">Students will apply the concepts they have learned by adding the following functionality to an existing game:&nbsp;<br />\r\n● Adding collectible items. </span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">● Drawing a score to the screen.&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">Students will apply the concepts they have learned by adding the following functionality to an existing game:&nbsp;<br />\r\n● Adding collectible items. </span></span></strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">● Drawing a score to the screen.&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\r\n','/media/Lesson3-TeachersGuide.pdf',4,'',5,2,65,NULL),(139,'Biến Đếm Ngộ Nghĩnh','2019-04-28 16:55:27.453560','2019-04-28 16:55:27.453566',1,1,'<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">Introduce students to (local) variables and promote principles of good coding. Students will learn the following concepts.&nbsp;Students will take an existing behavior and modify it, so that it can be more easily reused across the game, thereby promoting good coding habits.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\">Introduce students to (local) variables and promote principles of good coding. Students will learn the following concepts.&nbsp;Students will take an existing behavior and modify it, so that it can be more easily reused across the game, thereby promoting good coding habits.&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;<br />\r\n&nbsp;</span></span></strong></p>\r\n','/media/Lesson4-TeachersGuide.pdf',5,'',5,2,65,NULL),(140,'Sân Khấu Trong Tynker ','2019-04-28 17:13:12.867587','2019-04-29 06:02:26.915103',25,1,'<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/2019/04/27/banner.png\" style=\"height:311px; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Sau khi ho&agrave;n th&agrave;nh sản phẩm lập tr&igrave;nh, &ldquo;<em>S&acirc;n khấu trong Tynker&rdquo; </em>l&agrave; nơi để c&aacute;c nh&agrave; lập tr&igrave;nh nh&iacute; tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y, ra mắt sản phẩm của m&igrave;nh. Tại đ&acirc;y, c&aacute;c em được ph&eacute;p tr&igrave;nh b&agrave;y tất cả những g&igrave; c&aacute;c em l&agrave;m được từ những bước tr&ecirc;n. </span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n','<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/2019/04/29/picture32.jpg\" style=\"height:244px; width:467px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><span style=\"font-size:36px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>S&Acirc;N KHẤU TRONG TYNKER</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>A. Mục ti&ecirc;u hoạt động</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">1- Hiểu được kh&aacute;i niệm s&acirc;n khấu trong Tynker l&agrave; g&igrave;.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">2- Nhận biết cấu tạo v&agrave; một số đặc điểm của s&acirc;n khấu trong Tynker.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">3- Th&agrave;nh thạo c&aacute;c thao t&aacute;c xử l&yacute; đối với s&acirc;n khấu trong Tynker.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>B. Video b&agrave;i giảng</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Phần 1</span></span></strong></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EGLi6wOPGNk\" style=\"width:100%; height:500px\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Phần 2</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Dg079Wg0VME\" style=\"width:100%; height:500px\"></iframe></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"color:#d35400\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Phần 3&nbsp;</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n','https://www.youtube.com/embed/AMVkIPl_t4c',5,'',7,3,58,154),(141,'Tynker - Người Bạn Mới','2019-04-28 23:10:20.275491','2019-04-28 23:10:20.275496',5,1,'<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/2019/04/27/banner.png\" style=\"height:311px; width:600px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">