ify\"><span style=\"font-size:20px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">Scratch l&agrave; một ng&ocirc;n ngữ lập tr&igrave;nh Trực quan, gi&uacute;p người học dễ d&agrave;ng sử dụng c&aacute;c khối lệnh bằng c&aacute;ch k&eacute;o thả v&agrave; lắp gh&eacute;p th&agrave;nh kịch bản điều khiển đối tượng tr&ecirc;n s&acirc;n khấu th&ocirc;ng quan phần mềm Scratch. Lập tr&igrave;nh Scratch kh&ocirc;ng chỉ gi&uacute;p trẻ em ph&aacute;t triển tư duy m&agrave; c&ograve;n gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c em h&igrave;nh th&agrave;nh nhiều đức t&iacute;nh tốt để trở th&agrave;nh một c&ocirc;ng d&acirc;n th&agrave;nh đạt tr&ecirc;n phạm vi to&agrave;n cầu. Scratch cũng gi&uacute;p cho Gi&aacute;o vi&ecirc;n soạn ra c&aacute;c b&agrave;i giảng tương t&aacute;c trực quan, dễ hiểu.</span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n','','https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZUM03HvF0UI',8,'',7,3,107,NULL),(214,'Hướng dẫn cài đặt','2019-05-07 10:18:20.615285','2019-05-07 10:28:33.369916',16,1,'<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Lesson provides instructions on how to download, install, and run Alice 2.4. The installation process is simple, but Alice does not have an installer, so if you are unfamiliar with how to unzip a file, you may need a bit of help.</span></span></p>\r\n','','https://www.youtube.com/embed/UwXNAIrVzqU',1,'',6,3,108,NULL),(215,'Adding Objects and Subparts','2019-05-07 10:25:16.867268','2019-05-07 10:28:12.521683',30,1,'<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Lesson&nbsp;provides examples of adding objects to Alice World and positioning them how you&#39;d like them. Button Limiters such as &quot;Move Freely&quot;, &quot;Move Objects Up and Down&quot;, &quot;Resize Objects&quot;, and &quot;Duplicate Objects&quot; are used along with several others. In addition, the video shows how to use the objects panel to see the subparts of an object and how to manipulate those subparts. ed Alice techniques, functions, and methods.</span></span></p>\r\n','','https://www.youtube.com/embed/67jdgG-eAw0',1,'',6,3,109,NULL),(216,'Basic Camera Controls','2019-05-07 10:26:11.671573','2019-05-07 10:27:46.960667',10,1,'<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Lesson&nbsp;demonstrates how to use the Camera Control Arrows to move the camera in all directions. The camera can move in all six directions (Up, Down, Left, Right, Forward, Backward) as well as turn and tilt. The camera controls can be a bit tricky at first, but with practice, positioning the camera will become second nature.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n','','https://www.youtube.com/embed/WQqqmgpPdxk',2,'',6,3,109,NULL),(217,'Quad View and Object Positioning','2019-05-07 10:27:31.087849','2019-05-07 10:27:31.087856',10,1,'<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Lesson&nbsp;introduces how to properly place objects in a scene using Quad View. This is particularly important to master when trying to position two objects in relation to one another, such as a person holding a musical instrument or a knight holding a weapon. The Alice camera can create some optical illusions since it 3D objects are displayed on a 2D space. Using these concepts will help make scene creation easier for bigger animations.</span></span></p>\r\n','','https://www.youtube.com/embed/epL5bBaVWyU',3,'',6,3,109,NULL),(218,'Method Based Object Movement','2019-05-07 10:29:20.633893','2019-05-07 10:29:20.633899',15,1,'<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Lesson&nbsp;adds more tools for moving and manipulating objects on the screen to set up an initial scene. Using method based movement, you can manipulate objects by clicking on specific subparts and also selected a fixed amount of movement. Instead of guessing at moving an object by 5 meters, this method allows you to input a specific distance in a specific direction. This lesson ties in closely with Lesson 5.1 and 5.2, which uses these same concepts in simple animation.</span></span></p>\r\n','','https://www.youtube.com/embed/7ERIFYs4lOc',4,'',6,3,109,NULL),(219,'Lighting, Opacity, and Fog Properties','2019-05-07 10:43:27.485796','2019-05-07 10:43:27.485803',15,1,'<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Lesson centers on world and object properties in the properties tab. The three that are addressed here are world lighting and world fog properties, as well as object opacity. The use of atmosphere color and lighting are also discussed with reference to their impact on your world.</span></span></p>\r\n','','https://www.youtube.com/embed/X3IRwsbi5NM',1,'',6,3,110,NULL),(220,'Building an Undersea World','2019-05-07 10:44:12.861032','2019-05-07 10:44:12.861038',15,1,'<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Lesson&nbsp;uses fog and world color properties to create a scene representing the ocean bottom. Objects from the core gallery such as coral, seaweed, fish, and a shark are added, along with a volcano from the Hawaii category. This scene demonstrates using world properties to make a more realistic looking scene than traditional Alice programs.</span></span></p>\r\n','','https://www.youtube.com/embed/H8v8kkAfzGM',2,'',6,3,110,NULL),(221,'Cài đặt Alice','2019-05-07 16:02:44.613136','2019-05-07 16:02:44.613142',10,1,'<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><strong><u><span style=\"color:#2980b9\">Mục ti&ecirc;u:</span></u></strong> Gi&uacute;p học vi&ecirc;n c&agrave;i đặt v&agrave; khởi động Alice.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><strong><u><span style=\"color:#27ae60\">Y&ecirc;u cầu đầu ra:</span></u></strong> Học vi&ecirc;n c&agrave;i đặt v&agrave; khởi động th&agrave;nh c&ocirc;ng Alice.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><strong><u><span style=\"color:#16a085\">M&ocirc; tả:</span></u></strong>&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color:white\">Hoạt động C&Agrave;I ĐẶT ALICE&nbsp;&nbsp;sẽ gồm c&oacute;: </span><span style=\"background-color:white\"><strong>Video hướng dẫn chi tiết</strong></span><span style=\"background-color:white\">, </span><span style=\"background-color:white\"><strong>1 b&agrave;i giảng tương t&aacute;c</strong></span><span style=\"background-color:white\"> với gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c bạn c&oacute; thể dễ d&agrave;ng nắm bắt kiến thức trong video.</span></span></span></p>\r\n','<p style=\"margin-left:0in; margin-right:0in\"><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;\"><span style=\"background-color:white\">Hoạt động C&Agrave;I ĐẶT ALICE sẽ gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c bạn tải v&agrave; c&agrave;i đặt Alice</span></span></span></p>\r\n','/media/unzip/Hoat_dong_1_AElEbG4/story_flash.html  https://www.youtube.com/embed/6iQLb1zqd9k',1,'',6,7,23,NULL),(222,'Nộp bài','2019-05-09 09:08:39.737444','2019-05-09 11:52:33.757585',5,1,'<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#2980b9\"><u><strong>C&aacute;ch nộp:</strong></u></span> C&aacute;c bạn nộp bạn dưới dạng .zip</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">&nbsp; Hướng dẫn lưu zip:</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/jEj-JsZYOBA\" style=\"width:100%;height:500px\" width=\"500\"></iframe></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#27ae60\"><u><strong>Hướng dẫn đặt t&ecirc;n:</strong></u></span> Hoten_Chude3.zip</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">&nbsp; &nbsp;<u><em>V&iacute; dụ:</em></u> NguyenVanA_Chude3.zip</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:18px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><u><strong>K&iacute;ch thước:</strong></u></span> <span style=\"color:#e74c3c\"><strong>&lt;= 30MB</strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n','','',3,'',6,6,30,NULL);
