INSERT INTO `projectshare` VALUES (1,'ĐÈN LED MA THUẬT','Dùng  Arduino để điều khiển đèn Led sáng- tắt là một điều khá đơn giản. VẬn dụng nó, chúng ta có thể tạo ra những thứ tuyệt vời như mô phỏng đèn tín hiệu giao thông chẳng hạn!','<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:red\">L&Agrave;M M&Ocirc; H&Igrave;NH Đ&Egrave;N T&Iacute;N HIỆU ĐƠN GIẢN VỚI ATTINY13</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom:solid #1ba1e2 1.5pt; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/media/2019/04/28/b2cc17f677d0c8e8f51e06f206e3624b.jpg\" style=\"height:515px; width:650px\" /></p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;<strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:darkorange\">Giới thiệu</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">S&aacute;ng sớm n&agrave;o đi ra ng&otilde; phố, điều đầu ti&ecirc;n c&aacute;c bạn chạm tr&aacute;ng ch&iacute;nh l&agrave; d&ograve;ng người qua lại tấp nập. Với d&ograve;ng người v&agrave; phương tiện đ&ocirc;ng đ&uacute;c như thế th&igrave; sẽ thật sự hỗn loạn nếu bất kỳ ai cũng c&oacute; thể di chuyển theo &yacute; muốn của m&igrave;nh. Cần thiết phải c&oacute; 1 c&ocirc;ng cụ hỗ trợ cho c&aacute;c chủ c&ocirc;ng an giao th&ocirc;ng trong việc điều hướng người đi lại, ch&iacute;nh v&igrave; lẽ đ&oacute; m&agrave; Đ&egrave;n giao th&ocirc;ng ra đời. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Đ&egrave;n giao th&ocirc;ng đ&atilde; qu&aacute; quen thuộc với c&aacute;c bạn phải kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o. Với những &aacute;nh đ&egrave;n đầy m&agrave;u sắc n&agrave;y, bạn c&oacute; tạo th&agrave;nh một cột đ&egrave;n giao th&ocirc;ng cực k&igrave; đơn giản cho sa b&agrave;n của bạn. H&ocirc;m nay, ch&uacute;ng ta sẽ d&agrave;nh ra khoảng 20 ph&uacute;t để l&agrave;m mạch đ&egrave;n đầy s&aacute;ng tạo n&agrave;y nh&eacute;. Qua b&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y, hi vọng bạn sẽ học c&aacute;ch sử dụng <strong>ATTiny13</strong> để lập tr&igrave;nh những ứng dụng y&ecirc;u cầu k&iacute;ch thước b&eacute; nh&eacute;.</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:darkorange\">Kiến thức cần biết</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://arduino.vn/bai-viet/169-bai-2-attiny13-tro-thu-dac-luc-cua-arduino-lap-trinh-no\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#2086bf\">Lập tr&igrave;nh vi điều khiển ATTiny13 bằng Arduino</span></span></span></a></span></span></li>\r\n</ol>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:darkorange\">Phần cứng</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#262626\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://arduino.vn/bai-viet/42-arduino-uno-r3\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:white\">Arduino Uno</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#262626\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://k1.arduino.vn/img/2014/05/28/0/517_1231-1401211379-0--breadboard.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:white\">Breadboard</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#262626\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><a href=\"http://machtudong.vn/image/cache/data/dung-cu-khac/cap/breadboard-cable-65-500x500.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:white\">D&acirc;y cắm breadboard</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#262626\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">3 điện trở&nbsp;</span></span><a href=\"http://k2.arduino.vn/img/2014/05/27/0/481_8821-1401207510-0-resistor560ohm.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:white\">560 Ohm</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;(hoặc&nbsp;</span></span><a href=\"http://k2.arduino.vn/img/2014/05/27/0/482_8821-1401207697-0-220-ohms-5-axial-resistor.500x333.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:white\">220 Ohm</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;hoặc&nbsp;</span></span><a href=\"http://k3.arduino.vn/img/2014/05/27/0/484_8121-1401207819-0-1-kiloohm-5-axial-resistor.750x500.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:white\">1kOhm</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">)</span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#262626\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">3 đ&egrave;n LED m&agrave;u (</span></span><a href=\"http://k3.arduino.vn/img/2014/08/19/0/722_8121-1408450755-0-led-red.jpg\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#2086bf\">đỏ</span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">,&nbsp;</span></span><a href=\"http://k2.arduino.vn/img/2014/08/19/0/728_8821-1408450840-0-5mm-yellow-led.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:white\">v&agrave;ng</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">,&nbsp;</span></span><a href=\"http://k3.arduino.vn/img/2014/08/19/0/723_8121-1408450884-0-led-5mm-green-460x460.png\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:white\">xanh</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">)</span></span></span></span></span></li>\r\n	<li><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"color:#262626\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">1&nbsp;</span></span><a href=\"http://k1.arduino.vn/img/2014/06/14/0/604_12320-1402728667-0-attiny13.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:white\">ATTiny13</span></span></span></span></a></span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:darkorange\">Lắp mạch</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><img src=\"/media/2019/04/28/image.png\" style=\"height:585px; width:350px\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:darkorange\">Lập tr&igrave;nh v&agrave; giải th&iacute;ch</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Mục đ&iacute;ch của b&agrave;i n&agrave;y l&agrave; gi&uacute;p c&aacute;c bạn thực h&agrave;nh với vi điều khiển ATTiny13, v&igrave; vậy phần lập tr&igrave;nh v&ocirc; c&ugrave;ng đơn giản, v&agrave; chỉ bao gồm c&aacute;c h&agrave;m&nbsp;</span></span></span><a href=\"http://arduino.vn/reference/pinmode\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">pinMode</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">,&nbsp;</span></span></span><a href=\"http://arduino.vn/reference/delay\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">delay</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">&nbsp;v&agrave;&nbsp;</span></span></span><a href=\"http://arduino.vn/reference/digitalwrite\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-size:10.0pt\"><span style=\"background-color:#1ba1e2\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">digitalWrite</span></span></span></span></a><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">! </span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">int greenled = 0;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">int yellowled = 1;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">int redled = 4;</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">void setup()</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">{</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; //pinMode c&aacute;c đ&egrave;n led</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp; </span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; pinMode(greenled, OUTPUT);</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; pinMode(yellowled, OUTPUT);</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; pinMode(redled, OUTPUT);</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; // c&agrave;i đặt timer</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; TCCR0B |=&nbsp; _BV(CS02)&nbsp; ; </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">}</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">void _delay(word time = 1) { // X&acirc;y dựng lại h&agrave;m delay</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; for (word i = 1; i&lt;=time;i++) {</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; delayMicroseconds(150);</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; }</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">}</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">void loop()</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">{</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; digitalWrite(greenled, HIGH); //Bật đ&egrave;n xanh trong 5 gi&acirc;y</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; _delay(5000);</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; digitalWrite(greenled, LOW); //Tắt đ&egrave;n xanh, bật đ&egrave;n v&agrave;ng trong 1 gi&acirc;y</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; digitalWrite(yellowled, HIGH);</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; _delay(1000);</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; digitalWrite(yellowled, LOW); //tắt đ&egrave;n v&agrave;ng bật đ&egrave;n đỏ trong 5 gi&acirc;y</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; digitalWrite(redled, HIGH);</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; _delay(5000);</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">&nbsp; digitalWrite(redled,LOW);//Tắt đ&egrave;n đỏ</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Courier New&quot;\">}</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Khi bạn &quot;l&ecirc;n mạch&quot; th&igrave; n&oacute; đơn giản như thế n&agrave;y n&egrave; :D</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><img src=\"/media/2019/04/28/image_jiq3ePp.png\" style=\"height:270px; width:624px\" /><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:darkorange\">Kết luận</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#8e44ad\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">Con m&egrave;o n&oacute; k&ecirc;u meo meo, đ&oacute; l&agrave; điều hiển nhi&ecirc;n phải kh&ocirc;ng n&agrave;o? V&igrave; vậy chuyện thất bại ở những lần đầu thực h&agrave;nh l&agrave; điều kh&ocirc;ng thể tr&aacute;nh được. Đừng lo lắng, bạn đ&atilde; c&oacute; mục ti&ecirc;u, việc cần l&agrave;m b&acirc;y giờ l&agrave; theo đuổi mục ti&ecirc;u n&agrave;y&hellip; c&oacute; cố gắng l&agrave; l&agrave;m được ngay th&ocirc;i, hi vọng qua b&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y, bạn sẽ c&agrave;ng ho&agrave;n thiện c&aacute;c kĩ năng của m&igrave;nh v&agrave; ho&agrave;n thiện c&aacute;c dự &aacute;n t&aacute;o bạo hơn!</span></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color:#e74c3c\">&nbsp; Tham khảo Arduino.vn</span></span></span></p>\r\n','/media/psd-hand-drawn-traffic-icon-traffic-lights-heypik-6JU45XV.jpg','2019-04-28 17:10:57.800768','2019-04-28 17:10:57.800773',17,0,'',1,'',5,3),(2,'NHIỆT KẾ THỜI 4.0','Với dự án \" Nhiệt kế thời 4.0\" chúng ta có thể tạo ra cho mình một thiết bị kiểm tra nhiệt độ phòng và hiển thị nó ra màn hình LCD. ','<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:48px\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:red\">ĐỌC NHIỆT ĐỘ - ĐỘ ẨM V&Agrave; XUẤT RA M&Agrave;N H&Igrave;NH LCD</span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<div style=\"border-bottom:solid #1ba1e2 1.5pt; padding:0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm\">\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:darkorange\">1. Giới thiệu</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><em><span style=\"color:#16a085\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">B&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y sẽ hướng dẫn c&aacute;c bạn c&aacute;ch đọc nhiệt độ - độ ẩm từ cảm biến v&agrave; xuất ra m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh LCD. Hy vọng rằng qua b&agrave;i viết n&agrave;y, bạn sẽ dần hiểu được Arduino tạo cho người d&ugrave;ng một sự đơn giản v&agrave; tiện lợi đến mức n&agrave;o.</span></span></span></span></span></em></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:18.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:darkorange\">2. Nội dung ch&iacute;nh</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:13.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#16a085\">Đọc dữ liệu từ cảm biến nhiệt độ - độ ẩm DHT11</span><a href=\"http://arduino.vn/bai-viet/91-doc-nhiet-d