cute;n hay!</p>\n','2019-05-08 21:14:09.552420','2019-05-08 21:14:09.552425',1,'',42,5),(19,'<p>Hay!</p>\n','2019-05-08 21:14:22.277499','2019-05-08 21:14:22.277504',1,'',42,4),(20,'<p>Dự &aacute;n hấp dẫn!</p>\n','2019-05-08 21:14:38.171068','2019-05-08 21:14:38.171073',1,'',42,3),(21,'<p>Dự &aacute;n th&uacute; vị!</p>\n','2019-05-08 21:14:54.150762','2019-05-08 21:14:54.150769',1,'',42,2),(22,'<p>dự &aacute;n thật th&uacute; vị. t&ocirc;i kh&ocirc;ng ngờ, với Tynker m&igrave;nh c&oacute; thể tạo ra 1 tr&ograve; chơi m&ocirc; phỏng thực tế như vậy</p>\n','2019-05-08 23:25:40.588383','2019-05-08 23:25:40.588388',1,'',37,5),(23,'<p>du an hay hap dan</p>\n','2019-05-09 10:57:40.840299','2019-05-09 10:57:40.840304',1,'',38,6),(24,'<p>Rất th&iacute;ch dự &aacute;n n&agrave;y!</p>\n','2019-05-09 10:58:04.921765','2019-05-09 10:58:04.921771',1,'',38,5),(25,'<p>hấp dẫn v&agrave; l&ocirc;i cuốn</p>\n','2019-05-09 10:58:43.045625','2019-05-09 10:58:43.045632',1,'',38,1),(26,'<p>&yacute; nghĩa v&agrave; thu h&uacute;t người học. cung cấp nhiều nội dung kiến thức quan trọng</p>\n','2019-05-09 10:59:31.213011','2019-05-09 10:59:31.213018',1,'',38,2);
